reviews.text: I know a lot of people in Cbus are missing Neighbor's Deli. Frenchi's won't match the size of those Neighbor's sandwiches, but they will match - and even...

Ordered Le Eiffel Tower, a gyro and the croque monsier 
Unfrenchness aside (no French bread, no Dijon or brown mustard), if I evaluate it as a sandwich shop...
Let me tell you! I rarely start a review by saying... GET THERE! That's it... just get there! You will NOT find an authentic deli like this... fresh...
